      <title>२२ अध्यात्मम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/22_adhyAtmam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/22_adhyAtmam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/08/22/01_adhyAtmikAnyogAnanutiShThennyAyasaMhitAnanaishchArikAn.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अध्यात्मिकान् योगान् अनुतिष्ठेन् न्याय-संहितान् अनैश्चारिकान् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/08/22/01_adhyAtmikAnyogAnanutiShThennyAyasaMhitAnanaishchArikAn.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः …{Loading}…&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;He shall employ the means which tend to the acquisition of (the knowledge of) the Ātman, which are attended by the consequent (destruction of the passions, and) which prevent the wandering (of the mind from its object, and fix it on the contemplation of the Ātman). &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;अध्यात्मिकान् योगाननुतिष्ठेन्न्यायसंहिताननैश्चारिकान् ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;टीका&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;उक्तानि पतनीयान्यशुचिकराणि च कर्माणि । तेषां प्रायश्चित्तानि वक्ष्यन्नादित आत्मज्ञानं तदुपयोगिनश्च योगानधिकुरुते । तस्यापि सर्वपापहरत्वेन मुख्यप्रायश्चित्तत्वात् । श्रूयते हि—&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:2&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;भिद्यते हृदयग्रन्थिश्छिद्यन्ते सर्वसंशयाः।&#xA;क्षीयन्ते चास्य कर्माणि तस्मिन् दृष्टे परावरे ॥ इति ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:3&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:3&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; &amp;lsquo;तद्यथेषीकातूलमग्नौ प्रोतं प्रदूयेतेवं हाऽस्य सर्वे पाप्मानः प्रदूयन्त&amp;rsquo; इति च । याज्ञवल्क्योऽप्याह —&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:4&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:4&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;इज्याचारदमाहिंसादानस्वाध्यायकर्मणाम् ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;अयं तु परमो धर्मो यद्योगनाऽऽत्मदर्शनम् ॥ इति ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>२३ अध्यात्मम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/23_adhyAtmam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/1/08/23_adhyAtmam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/08/23/01_Atman_pashyan_sarvabhUtAni.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;आत्मन् पश्यन् सर्वभूतानि न मुह्येच्चिन्तयन्कविः । आत्मानं चैव सर्वत्र यः पश्येत्स वै ब्रह्मा नाकपृष्ठे विराजति १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/08/23/01_Atman_pashyan_sarvabhUtAni.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः …{Loading}…&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;That Brāhmaṇa, who is wise and recognises all creatures to be in the Ātman, who pondering (thereon) does not become bewildered, and who recognises the Ātman in every (created) thing, shines, indeed, in heaven.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;आत्मन् पश्यन् सर्वभूतानि न मुह्येच्चिन्तयन्कविः।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;आत्मानं चैव सर्वत्र यः पश्यत्स वै ब्रह्मा नाकपृष्ठे विराजति ॥ ९ ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
